messages.messageBody:
It's not finished yet, but here's an early peek if you want at the
artwork for the upcoming holiday:

http://sandradodd.com/learnnothingday/artinprogress


I might never catch up with e-mail, but we had a good time working on
this. Holly will finish it tonight and tomorrow, I think. She's off
taking her boyfriend from a day's work at the comic book store to a
World of Warcraft raid. His sister has his car. She'll be back.
But I'm glad she let me share some of the progress and the plan.

Sandra
